946
00:58:54,019 --> 00:58:56,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ona treba mijenjati ljude.

947
00:58:56,019 --> 00:58:58,119
[SPEAKER_01] A promijenjeni pojedinci

948
00:58:58,119 --> 00:58:59,920
[SPEAKER_01] trebaju ići u gospodarstvo,

949
00:58:59,920 --> 00:59:00,860
[SPEAKER_01] u politiku, u sport,

950
00:59:00,860 --> 00:59:01,980
[SPEAKER_01] gdje već žele.

951
00:59:01,980 --> 00:59:04,960
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da politika ima svoje mjesto.

952
00:59:04,960 --> 00:59:06,719
[SPEAKER_01] Nažalost, u pravu ste

953
00:59:06,719 --> 00:59:08,699
[SPEAKER_01] danas baš zbog toga

954
00:59:08,699 --> 00:59:11,739
[SPEAKER_01] što nemamo vrijednostni sustav dobar,

955
00:59:11,739 --> 00:59:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] nemamo ni političare dobre.

956
00:59:14,000 --> 00:59:17,119
[SPEAKER_01] A ovo što vi činite,

957
00:59:17,119 --> 00:59:20,780
[SPEAKER_01] to je zalog za budućnost.

958
00:59:20,780 --> 00:59:23,420
[SPEAKER_01] I niće to biti za šest mjeseci,

959
00:59:23,420 --> 00:59:24,460
[SPEAKER_01] godinu, dvije.

960
00:59:24,460 --> 00:59:25,900
[SPEAKER_01] To će trajati.

961
00:59:25,900 --> 00:59:27,679
[SPEAKER_01] To će trajati.

962
00:59:27,679 --> 00:59:29,300
[SPEAKER_01] I nemojmo ni očekivati

963
00:59:29,300 --> 00:59:30,639
[SPEAKER_01] da bude za godinu, za dvije.

964
00:59:30,639 --> 00:59:32,059
[SPEAKER_01] Mi pred svake izbore

965
00:59:32,059 --> 00:59:34,340
[SPEAKER_01] imamo nekakve priče,

966
00:59:34,340 --> 00:59:34,920
[SPEAKER_01] sad će,

967
00:59:34,920 --> 00:59:36,679
[SPEAKER_01] to je najvažniji trenutak

968
00:59:36,679 --> 00:59:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] u hrvatskoj povijesti.

969
00:59:38,000 --> 00:59:39,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ako sada ne uspijemo,

970
00:59:39,380 --> 00:59:40,800
[SPEAKER_01] nećemo nikada uspjeti.

971
00:59:40,800 --> 00:59:42,039
[SPEAKER_01] To je najbitnije.

972
00:59:42,039 --> 00:59:43,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ma molim vas,

973
00:59:43,880 --> 00:59:45,340
[SPEAKER_01] prvo treba ovdje gusliti

974
00:59:45,340 --> 00:59:46,599
[SPEAKER_01] ovo što vi činite,

975
00:59:46,599 --> 00:59:48,719
[SPEAKER_01] pa iznutra se formirati.

976
00:59:49,199 --> 00:59:50,500
[SPEAKER_01] niko više takvog čovjeka

977
00:59:50,500 --> 00:59:51,840
[SPEAKER_01] u saboru ne može okrenut.

978
00:59:51,840 --> 01:00:06,019
[SPEAKER_05] još jedno, još jedno.

979
01:00:06,019 --> 01:00:06,440
[SPEAKER_05] prekati.

980
01:00:06,440 --> 01:00:07,780
[SPEAKER_05] Evo tamo,

981
01:00:07,780 --> 01:00:08,480
[SPEAKER_05] ma je skupo.

982
01:00:08,480 --> 01:00:13,119
[SPEAKER_05] ja ću kratko.

983
01:00:13,119 --> 01:00:21,579
[SPEAKER_02] ja ću kratko.

984
01:00:21,579 --> 01:00:31,500
[SPEAKER_00] joj.

985
01:00:31,500 --> 01:00:36,079
[SPEAKER_01] Znate,

986
01:00:36,079 --> 01:00:37,719
[SPEAKER_01] osjećam se kriv.

987
01:00:37,719 --> 01:00:39,920
[SPEAKER_01] Osjećam se tu

988
01:00:39,920 --> 01:00:42,579
[SPEAKER_01] ne dorastao.

989
01:00:42,579 --> 01:00:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] u našem životu

990
01:00:49,000 --> 01:00:51,039
[SPEAKER_01] smo mi trudili se,

991
01:00:51,039 --> 01:00:51,840
[SPEAKER_01] nastojali,

992
01:00:51,840 --> 01:00:52,760
[SPEAKER_01] ali mislim

993
01:00:52,760 --> 01:00:55,239
[SPEAKER_01] da možda ponekad

994
01:00:55,239 --> 01:00:56,619
[SPEAKER_01] ne u dovoljnoj mjeri

995
01:00:56,619 --> 01:00:58,420
[SPEAKER_01] i ponekad ne

996
01:00:58,420 --> 01:01:00,480
[SPEAKER_01] na dovoljan isprava način.

997
01:01:01,440 --> 01:01:03,400
[SPEAKER_01] Trudimo se sad to ispravljati

998
01:01:03,400 --> 01:01:05,880
[SPEAKER_01] i to je strahovito važno.

999
01:01:05,880 --> 01:01:06,980
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo što sam vam ja sad

1000
01:01:06,980 --> 01:01:08,039
[SPEAKER_01] malo prije rekao,

1001
01:01:08,039 --> 01:01:09,679
[SPEAKER_01] odnosi se i na mene.

1002
01:01:09,679 --> 01:01:12,559
[SPEAKER_01] Sve što sam rekao

1003
01:01:12,559 --> 01:01:13,380
[SPEAKER_01] i na mene.

1004
01:01:13,380 --> 01:01:14,980
[SPEAKER_01] Jer mi često

1005
01:01:14,980 --> 01:01:16,440
[SPEAKER_01] i vi isto tako

1006
01:01:16,440 --> 01:01:18,500
[SPEAKER_01] zapadnemo u jednu zamku.

1007
01:01:18,500 --> 01:01:20,639
[SPEAKER_01] Kad dođemo do nečega

1008
01:01:20,639 --> 01:01:22,199
[SPEAKER_01] što nas oduševi,

1009
01:01:22,199 --> 01:01:23,539
[SPEAKER_01] što nas pokrene,

1010
01:01:23,539 --> 01:01:25,440
[SPEAKER_01] onda se znamo opustiti.

1011
01:01:26,699 --> 01:01:28,380
[SPEAKER_01] Znamo to pustiti

1012
01:01:28,380 --> 01:01:29,579
[SPEAKER_01] i to nekako

1013
01:01:29,579 --> 01:01:32,079
[SPEAKER_01] pređe u zaborav,

1014
01:01:32,079 --> 01:01:35,039
[SPEAKER_01] obuzme nas ponekad

1015
01:01:35,039 --> 01:01:36,239
[SPEAKER_01] i gordost,

1016
01:01:36,239 --> 01:01:37,420
[SPEAKER_01] i taština,

1017
01:01:37,420 --> 01:01:38,940
[SPEAKER_01] i uspjeh.

1018
01:01:38,940 --> 01:01:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Uspjeh je vrlo često

1019
01:01:41,000 --> 01:01:44,500
[SPEAKER_01] najveći neprijatelj naš.

1020
01:01:44,500 --> 01:01:45,460
[SPEAKER_01] Vrlo često.

1021
01:01:45,460 --> 01:01:47,260
[SPEAKER_01] On nas nekako umiri,

1022
01:01:47,260 --> 01:01:48,179
[SPEAKER_01] zaveže

1023
01:01:48,179 --> 01:01:51,099
[SPEAKER_01] i stegne nas

1024
01:01:51,099 --> 01:01:51,760
[SPEAKER_01] i obveže

1025
01:01:51,760 --> 01:01:53,219
[SPEAKER_01] da uživamo u njemu

1026
01:01:53,219 --> 01:01:55,039
[SPEAKER_01] i ne trudimo se više i dalje.

1027
01:01:55,039 --> 01:01:56,679
[SPEAKER_01] A u duhovnosti je to

1028
01:01:56,679 --> 01:01:57,780
[SPEAKER_01] jako bitno.

1029
01:01:57,780 --> 01:02:00,139
[SPEAKER_01] I tu mi ovoga,

1030
01:02:00,139 --> 01:02:02,159
[SPEAKER_01] evo, pokušavamo to nadoknaditi

1031
01:02:02,159 --> 01:02:03,860
[SPEAKER_01] i popraviti se u tome.

1032
01:02:03,860 --> 01:02:07,260
[SPEAKER_00] Na sreću u braku je dvoje.

1033
01:02:07,260 --> 01:02:08,460
[SPEAKER_00] Muži, žena.

1034
01:02:08,460 --> 01:02:09,679
[SPEAKER_00] I onda...

1035
01:02:09,679 --> 01:02:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] I žene baš tako puno ne obuzima

1036
01:02:24,000 --> 01:02:25,579
[SPEAKER_00] briga oko posla.

1037
01:02:25,579 --> 01:02:28,039
[SPEAKER_00] ipak više bdije

1038
01:02:28,039 --> 01:02:29,039
[SPEAKER_00] nad obitelji,

1039
01:02:29,039 --> 01:02:30,960
[SPEAKER_00] nad svojim brakom,

1040
01:02:30,960 --> 01:02:34,659
[SPEAKER_00] nad našim duhovnim životom.

1041
01:02:34,659 --> 01:02:39,039
[SPEAKER_00] Mi u duhovni život ulažemo...

1042
01:02:39,039 --> 01:02:47,840
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam vam pričala priču od prilike kako je to bilo u onim godinama prije nego smo bili na bračnom vikendu.

1043
01:02:47,940 --> 01:02:51,400
[SPEAKER_00] zaista smo mi pomalo sve dalje dalje dalje dalje dalje dalje odlazili.

1044
01:02:51,400 --> 01:02:52,860
[SPEAKER_00] čak su naši prijatelji...

1045
01:02:52,860 --> 01:02:57,139
[SPEAKER_00] Danas ste čuli kakav si čovjek, takav ti je i prijatelj.

1046
01:02:57,139 --> 01:02:59,619
[SPEAKER_00] E, tako smo mi u to vrijeme.

1047
01:02:59,619 --> 01:03:03,659
[SPEAKER_00] Naši prijatelji nisu bili baš katolici svi,

1048
01:03:03,659 --> 01:03:07,760
[SPEAKER_00] nego smo mi imali vrlo šareno prijateljstvo.

1049
01:03:08,500 --> 01:03:11,739
[SPEAKER_00] tek ulaskom u zajednicu bračnih susreta,

1050
01:03:11,739 --> 01:03:16,920
[SPEAKER_00] ponovo smo one prijatelje iz mladosti, svjeronauka,

1051
01:03:16,920 --> 01:03:24,440
[SPEAKER_00] s njima počeli neke nove ljude upoznali koji su imali iste vrijednosti kao i mi.

1052
01:03:24,440 --> 01:03:27,119
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, uvijek su te vrijednosti u nama bile.

1053
01:03:27,119 --> 01:03:31,619
[SPEAKER_00] Samo nekad smo im dozvolili da dođu više do izražaja, nekad manje.

1054
01:03:31,619 --> 01:03:37,119
[SPEAKER_00] E sad, kad smo se mi ponovo počeli vraćati tim svojim vrijednostima,

1055
01:03:38,260 --> 01:03:43,900
[SPEAKER_00] promijenili smo društvo, pomalo smo počeli sve više i češće se moliti.

1056
01:03:43,900 --> 01:03:48,159
[SPEAKER_00] Sve više i više je molitva dolazila među nas

1057
01:03:48,159 --> 01:03:50,699
[SPEAKER_00] i onda se to pomalo počelo mijenjati.

1058
01:03:50,699 --> 01:03:54,300
[SPEAKER_00] I onda u jednom trenutku, ponovo ponavljam,

1059
01:03:54,300 --> 01:03:59,420
[SPEAKER_00] taj jedan protestant ulazi u naš život.

1060
01:03:59,420 --> 01:04:04,579
[SPEAKER_00] Mi ga angažiramo tamo da on našim ljudima predaje etiku poslovanja,

1061
01:04:04,980 --> 01:04:10,719
[SPEAKER_00] dogovorimo s njim, dogovorimo cijenu za to sve skupa i u muževoj kancelariji

1062
01:04:10,719 --> 01:04:16,639
[SPEAKER_00] na stroje i sad on ne kaže, e sad kad smo se ovako lijepo dogovorili,

1063
01:04:16,639 --> 01:04:18,460
[SPEAKER_00] idemo zahvaliti gospodinu.

1064
01:04:18,460 --> 01:04:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] I on nas uhvati za ruke, kancelarija sa staklima okolo,

1065
01:04:23,000 --> 01:04:26,340
[SPEAKER_00] svi nas mogu gledati, i on nas uhvati za ruke,

1066
01:04:26,340 --> 01:04:29,900
[SPEAKER_00] spusti glavu i počne zahvaljivati gospodinu.

1067
01:04:30,179 --> 01:04:35,920
[SPEAKER_00] I to dosta dugo, nekih pet minuta, i mi smo ovako u kancelariji,

1068
01:04:35,920 --> 01:04:38,659
[SPEAKER_00] u našoj, u službenoj, je vidio nas tamo...

1069
01:04:38,659 --> 01:04:39,659
[SPEAKER_01] I meni je bilo neugodno.

1070
01:04:39,659 --> 01:04:43,880
[SPEAKER_00] Vidi nas tamo dvadesetak ljudi.

1071
01:04:43,880 --> 01:04:47,699
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, to je bio takav prelom u našem životu.

1072
01:04:47,699 --> 01:04:49,659
[SPEAKER_00] To je toliko promijenilo.

1073
01:04:49,659 --> 01:04:53,659
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nas, katolike, da jedan protestant uči,

1074
01:04:53,659 --> 01:04:57,659
[SPEAKER_00] to je, stvarno smo se posramili.

1075
01:04:58,460 --> 01:05:00,400
[SPEAKER_00] Zaista smo se posramili.

1076
01:05:00,400 --> 01:05:03,599
[SPEAKER_00] Neka je kamera, ali i ovo je istina.

1077
01:05:03,599 --> 01:05:08,480
[SPEAKER_00] I to je, to je puno sad već godina,

1078
01:05:08,480 --> 01:05:14,239
[SPEAKER_00] i od tog trenutka smo mi i počeli na Kristofore odlaziti,

1079
01:05:14,239 --> 01:05:18,619
[SPEAKER_00] sprijateljili se sa Lončarom, Josipom.

1080
01:05:18,619 --> 01:05:22,940
[SPEAKER_00] Mi danas, u ovo vrijeme, jednom tjedno,

1081
01:05:22,940 --> 01:05:26,139
[SPEAKER_00] imamo kod nas, u radno vrijeme,

1082
01:05:26,820 --> 01:05:28,980
[SPEAKER_00] dva sata razmatranja Biblije.

1083
01:05:28,980 --> 01:05:31,360
[SPEAKER_00] Sa još jednim bračnim parom

1084
01:05:31,360 --> 01:05:33,699
[SPEAKER_00] i sa Josipom Lončarom.

1085
01:05:33,699 --> 01:05:36,340
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki utorak u jutro

1086
01:05:36,340 --> 01:05:39,940
[SPEAKER_00] on dođe kod nas tamo.

1087
01:05:39,940 --> 01:05:42,340
